<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kanagara Creative</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;}
body{background:#0f0f0f;color:#fff;overflow-x:hidden;}

header{
  position:fixed;
  width:100%;
  top:0;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
  backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
  padding:15px 50px;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  z-index:999;
}

header h2{color:#fff;}

nav a{
  color:#fff;
  margin-left:20px;
  text-decoration:none;
}

.hero{
  height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  text-align:center;
  background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.7),rgba(0,0,0,.7)),
  url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505236858219-8359eb29e329');
  background-size:cover;
}

.hero h1{
  font-size:60px;
  animation:fadeUp 1s ease;
}

.hero p{
  margin-top:15px;
  opacity:.8;
}

.btn{
  display:inline-block;
  margin-top:25px;
  padding:12px 30px;
  background:#ff4d5a;
  color:#fff;
  border-radius:30px;
  text-decoration:none;
}

.section{
  padding:100px 50px;
  text-align:center;
}

.services{
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  justify-content:center;
}

.card{
  background:#1a1a1a;
  padding:30px;
  margin:15px;
  width:280px;
  border-radius:15px;
  transition:.3s;
}

.card:hover{
  transform:translateY(-10px);
  background:#ff4d5a;
}

.portfolio{
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  justify-content:center;
}

.portfolio img{
  width:300px;
  margin:10px;
  border-radius:10px;
}

footer{
  background:#000;
  text-align:center;
  padding:20px;
}

@keyframes fadeUp{
  from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(50px);}
  to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h2>KANAGARA</h2>
  <nav>
    <a href="#home">Home</a>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div>
    <h1>Creative Agency & Event Organizer</h1>
    <p>Mewujudkan event dan brand yang berkelas</p>
    <a class="btn" href="#">Mulai Project</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="about">
  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <p>KANAGARA CREATIVE adalah agency profesional yang bergerak di bidang Event Organizer dan Digital Creative dengan fokus pada kualitas dan inovasi.</p>
</section>

<section class="section" id="services">
  <h2>Services</h2>
  <div class="services">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Event Organizer</h3>
      <p>Wedding, konser, corporate event.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Digital Marketing</h3>
      <p>Social media, ads, branding.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Creative Production</h3>
      <p>Video, desain, konten kreatif.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="portfolio">
  <h2>Portfolio</h2>
  <div class="portfolio">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511578314322-379afb476865">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492684223066-81342ee5ff30">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505236858219-8359eb29e329">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="contact">
  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Hubungi kami sekarang</p>
  <a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/628xxxxxxx">WhatsApp</a>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Kanagara Creative</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
